    "description": "At IFA 2018, the edge-less screen went mainstream, with bezel-free designs making an appearance across the entire show with new computers from Dell, Acer, Asus, and Lenovo. The future has arrived, and its leaving the bezel behind for good.  Subscribe:   Like The Verge on Facebook:  Follow on Twitter:  Follow on Instagram:  Read More:  Community guidelines:   Subscribe to Verge Science on YouTube, a new home base for our explorations into the future of science:",
